    dc:description "Figures 94-105. Blackburneus furcatus (Schmidt, 1909) (Cunyaba [= Cuiabá], Mato Grosso, Brazil). 94-95) Habitus (morphological details and length ideogram). 96-97) Aedeagus (dorsal and lateral view). 98) Epipharynx. Blackburneus guatemalensis (Bates, 1887) (Ostuncalco, Quezaltenango, Guatemala). 99) Epipharynx. 100-101) Aedeagus (dorsal and lateral view). 102-104) Habitus (length ideogram and colour variations). 105) Habitus (morphological details)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10090559/files/figure.png" ;
